•Inferi Dominatus •</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulacerade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lacerade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Disciple</span><br>  Posts: 283<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(7/14/02 6:46:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=997.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: real evade key</span><hr size=1> I just turn off attack, step back a little bit and feign.  I think it works better then a button because you have more control over it and can use other hotkeys while this ones still going off.  Just personal preference for me, but stepping back a bit makes a huge difference and you can't do that with a hotkey. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=588>Lacerade</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukunntar02.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kunntar02</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(7/24/02 10:17:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=997.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: real evade key</span><hr size=1> i use a key i like to call de-aggro...<br>
